<section id="about-1" class="about-text">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row-fluid">
      <div class="col-sm-12">
        <p class="about" >Game Roster believes online games are more fun with great friends, reliable players that share common interests, and tight knit communities where members are more committed because they care. We help you find those players and build those communities that can grow beyond the limits of any game, system, or site.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row-fluid about-details">
      <div class="col-sm-3">
        <div class="row-fluid">
          <div class="col-sm-12 card-1">
            <h5>Limitless Communities</h5>
            <p>Filters, ratings, activity tracking, and algorithms help you discover the perfect community for your style. Join as many as you want or blaze a trail and create your own. Game Roster provides everything you need to organize and grow your clan.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-3">
        <div class="row-fluid">
          <div class="col-sm-12 card-2">
            <h5>Reliable Players</h5>
            <p>LFG sites and matchmaking hook you up with random people while Game Roster lets you build your own Community LFG<sup>SM</sup> so you quickly get players you screen and trust. Interactive rosters and invitations help you organize a great team.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-3">
        <div class="row-fluid">
          <div class="col-sm-12 card-3">
            <h5>Integrate</h5>
            <p>Gaming has gotten more complex with your information stored across multiple social platforms, game publisher sites, various game systems, and third party chat tools. We help you connect these in a central hub so users can easily navigate to your key sites and sponsors.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-3">
        <div class="row-fluid">
          <div class="col-sm-12 card-4">
            <h5>Other Great Stuff</h5>
            <p>Explore communities, players, public games, and other opportunities.  Set custom game alerts, automatically block players with preferences, screen members through applications, assign community roles, and send messages across all platforms.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
